{
  "stem": "20711.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I wouldn't be surprised if she did other illegal activity in her traveling and taking messages from different parts of the country from those people who were together my mother-- with my father, because she was constantly going.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And she came to see me maybe every second week or so for a day, and then off she goes.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "In her next visiting day, Aunt Teresa told her how petrified I am from the bombing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And she suggest, not because she was not willing to put up with me on a longer term, but maybe it would be better to find a more quiet, safer place.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So my mother started to look around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I am not sure, but I think Aunt Teresa recommended the next family, who  were called Hodi family, who had the habit of spending the summer months in a vacation, in a resort area, which was a very smart move.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Because during this restricted era, everybody had to report their address at the police station within 48 hours.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "If you made any move in any place, the first step you must take to report to the police, even if you was not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It was for everybody, for the whole population.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And the only exception for the rule were vacation places because people went to vacation not for 48 hours, but two weeks or possibly a months.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So it was one place I could be without had to register at least for a months.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So that was one of the major reasons my mother decided I will go with that family, who was willing to take me with them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "With a good lump sun money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And they even supplied me with a false identification as one of their nieces.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
